OL,5, Teachers have supported calls for all  
OL,6, school leaders to be given suicide     
OL,7, prevention training amid warnings of a 
OL,8, "mental health emergency".             
OL,10,FA motion was passed on Sunday at       
OL,11,Fteachers' union NASUWT's annual        
OL,12,Fconference in Harrogate.               
OL,14,FIt warned of a "rise in suicide,       
OL,15,Fsuicide attempts and suicidal thoughts 
OL,16,Fwithin the teaching profession".       
OL,18,FEducation watchdog Ofsted has faced    
OL,19,Fgreater scrutiny since the suicide of  
OL,20,Fheadteacher Ruth Perry.                
